00:23:16,150 --> 00:23:18,990
SPEAKER_17: I've paid the rent with mother's jewelry.

234
00:24:29,059 --> 00:24:31,960
SPEAKER_17: "Don't Gamble" is my son's name.

235
00:24:32,500 --> 00:24:33,789
SPEAKER_17: You mocking me?

236
00:24:33,859 --> 00:24:36,390
SPEAKER_17: No, his real name's Youqing.

237
00:24:37,329 --> 00:24:39,430
SPEAKER_17: Jiazhen came back with him.

238
00:24:39,539 --> 00:24:42,869
