326
00:36:33,750 --> 00:36:36,840
SPEAKER_17: Dying like this,
their families won't even know.

327
00:36:38,489 --> 00:36:39,719
SPEAKER_17: Fugui...

328
00:36:40,559 --> 00:36:42,889
SPEAKER_17: we've got to make it back alive.

342
00:42:44,389 --> 00:42:45,650
SPEAKER_17: Fengxia!

368
00:45:53,940 --> 00:45:56,070
SPEAKER_17: How come Fengxia can't talk?

369
00:45:57,380 --> 00:45:59,369
SPEAKER_17: She was fine when I left.

370
00:45:59,510 --> 00:46:01,679
SPEAKER_17: She can't even say "Daddy."

